# ---------------------------------------------------------------------------
# combined — __enter__, __exit__, __call__ across all 5 pathlib subjects
#
# 5 classes x 3 methods = 15 rows.
# All fifteen values are false; no pathlib class implements the context
# manager or callable protocols in its own __dict__.
# Path objects are immutable filesystem path value types; __enter__,
# __exit__, and __call__ are not part of the pathlib API.
# ---------------------------------------------------------------------------

